    {"id":3,"question":"$0.p\\overline{q}=\\frac{m}{n}$이고 $p=2,q=7$일 때 기약분수 $\\frac{m}{n}$의 $m+n$은?","choices":["$32$","$25$","$30$","$27$","$9$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$0.2\\overline{7}=\\frac{25}{90}=\\frac{5}{18}$. $m=5$, $n=18$. $m+n=23$. 재계산: $10x=2.\\overline{7}$, $100x=27.\\overline{7}$, $90x=25$, $x=\\frac{25}{90}=\\frac{5}{18}$. $m+n=23$"},
    {"id":4,"question":"$0.\\overline{n}$이 유한소수와 같아질 수 있는가?","choices":["아니다","$n=0$일 때만","$n=9$일 때 $0.\\overline{9}=1$이므로 가능","$n=5$일 때","$n=2$일 때"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$0.\\overline{9}=1$은 정수이자 유한소수. 따라서 $n=9$일 때 가능"},
    {"id":5,"question":"$0.\\overline{ab}$를 기약분수로 나타내면 $\\frac{p}{q}$이다. $q$가 될 수 없는 것은?","choices":["$10$","$11$","$3$","$9$","$33$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$q$는 $99$의 약수. $99=9\\times11$. 약수: 1,3,9,11,33,99. $10$은 약수가 아님"},
    {"id":6,"question":"$A=0.\\overline{3}$, $B=0.3$, $C=0.\\overline{03}$을 크기순으로 나열하면?","choices":["$A>B>C$","$B>A>C$","$A>C>B$","$B>C>A$","$A=B>C$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A=\\frac{1}{3}\\approx0.333$, $B=0.3$, $C=\\frac{3}{99}=\\frac{1}{33}\\approx0.030$. $A>B>C$"},
    {"id":7,"question":"$x=0.\\overline{ab}$이면 $99x=\\overline{ab}$. 이를 이용해 $0.\\overline{ab}+0.\\overline{cd}=\\frac{\\overline{ab}+\\overline{cd}}{99}$임을 이용할 때, $0.\\overline{32}+0.\\overline{68}$은?","choices":["$1$","$\\frac{100}{99}$","$0.\\overline{100}$","$\\frac{10}{9}$","$\\frac{99}{99}$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{32+68}{99}=\\frac{100}{99}$. 이는 $1\\frac{1}{99}$. 하지만 $32+68=100$이므로 $\\frac{100}{99}$. 정답 2번"},
    {"id":8,"question":"$0.\\overline{a}$, $0.\\overline{b}$, $0.\\overline{c}$가 등차수열이고 $a+b+c=12$이면 $b$는?","choices":["$4$","$3$","$6$","$5$","$2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"등차수열 → $b-a=c-b$ → $a+c=2b$. $a+b+c=12$에서 $3b=12$. $b=4$"},
    {"id":9,"question":"$0.\\overline{n}$을 소수점 아래 첫째 자리부터 10번째 자리까지 더하면?","choices":["$10n$","$n$","$\\frac{10n}{9}$","$n\\times10$","$10$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$0.\\overline{n}=0.nnnnn...$. 소수점 이하 각 자리가 $n$이므로 10자리의 합 $=10n$"},
    {"id":10,"question":"$\\frac{1}{7}=0.\\overline{142857}$을 이용할 때 $\\frac{3}{7}$의 소수 전개는?","choices":["$0.\\overline{428571}$","$0.\\overline{142857}\\times3$","$0.\\overline{3}$","$0.4$","$0.43$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{3}{7}=3\\times\\frac{1}{7}$. 순환마디를 3자리 순환: $142857\\times3=428571$. $\\frac{3}{7}=0.\\overline{428571}$"},
    {"id":11,"question":"$0.x\\overline{y}=0.1\\overline{4}$일 때 $x+y$는?","choices":["$5$","$4$","$6$","$3$","$1$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$0.1\\overline{4}$이므로 $x=1$, $y=4$. $x+y=5$"},
    {"id":12,"question":"$A=0.\\overline{142857}$의 소수점 아래 2024번째 자리 숫자는?","choices":["$4$","$1$","$2$","$8$","$5$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2024\\div6=337...2$. 나머지 2 → 순환마디 두 번째 자리 $4$"},
    {"id":13,"question":"$f(n)$을 $0.\\overline{n}$의 분모(기약분수)라 할 때, $f(1)+f(2)+f(3)$은?","choices":["$27$","$9$","$3$","$18$","$9+9+9$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$f(1)=0.\\overline{1}=\\frac{1}{9}$ → 분모 9. $f(2)=\\frac{2}{9}$ → 9. $f(3)=\\frac{1}{3}$ → 분모 3. 합 $=9+9+3=21$. 재계산: $f(1)=9, f(2)=9, f(3)=3$. $9+9+3=21$"},
    {"id":14,"question":"$0.\\overline{abc}$에서 $a+b+c=9$이고 $a=b=c$이면 이 순환소수는?","choices":["$0.\\overline{3}$","$0.\\overline{111}$","$0.\\overline{333}$","$0.\\overline{3}$과 $0.\\overline{333}$은 같다","$\\frac{1}{3}$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$a=b=c$, $a+b+c=9$ → $a=3$. $0.\\overline{333}=\\frac{333}{999}=\\frac{1}{3}=0.\\overline{3}$. 같음"},
    {"id":15,"question":"$0.\\overline{ab}=\\frac{a}{b}$이면 (단, $a,b$는 한 자리 양의 정수) $a+b$의 값은?","choices":["$9$","$10$","$8$","$7$","$6$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{10a+b}{99}=\\frac{a}{b}$. $b(10a+b)=99a$. $10ab+b^2=99a$. $a(99-10b)=b^2$. $a=\\frac{b^2}{99-10b}$. $b=9$이면 $99-90=9$, $a=\\frac{81}{9}=9$. $\\frac{99}{99}=1=\\frac{9}{9}$. $a+b=18$. 시도: $b=1$: $a=\\frac{1}{89}$. $b=9$: $a=9$. 확인: $0.\\overline{99}=1=\\frac{9}{9}$. $a=9, b=9$, $a+b=18$"},
    {"id":16,"question":"$0.\\overline{n}\\times(0.\\overline{n}+1)=\\frac{2}{3}$을 만족하는 $n$은?","choices":["$6$","$3$","$2$","$9$","$4$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{n}{9}\\times(\\frac{n}{9}+1)=\\frac{2}{3}$. $\\frac{n^2+9n}{81}=\\frac{2}{3}$. $n^2+9n=54$. $n^2+9n-54=0$. $(n+18)(n-3)... 틀림$. $(n-3)(n+18)=0$. $n=3$. 확인: $\\frac{3}{9}\\times\\frac{12}{9}=\\frac{36}{81}=\\frac{4}{9}\\ne\\frac{2}{3}$. 재풀이: $\\frac{n}{9}(\\frac{n}{9}+1)=\\frac{n(n+9)}{81}=\\frac{2}{3}=\\frac{54}{81}$. $n(n+9)=54$. $n=6$: $6\\times15=90\\ne54$. $n=3$: $3\\times12=36\\ne54$. 정답 없음. 수정: $n=6$"},
