    {"id":18,"question":"$0.\\overline{3}+0.\\overline{33}+0.\\overline{333}=$?","choices":["$\\frac{41}{111}$","$\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{1}{3}$","$1$","$\\frac{37}{99}$","$0.\\overline{999}$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{3}{9}+\\frac{33}{99}+\\frac{333}{999}=\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{1}{3}=1$. 그러나 $\\frac{33}{99}=\\frac{1}{3}$이고 $\\frac{333}{999}=\\frac{1}{3}$이므로 $=1$. 정답 3번"},
